law.text:
This title does not apply to:
a person while acting under a judgment or order of a court;
a public officer while performing the duties of office;
a person while engaging in a single transaction that involves the sale or lease of any real estate under a power of attorney executed by the owner of the real estate;
a licensed auctioneer while selling any real estate at public auction;
an owner or lessor of any real estate while managing, leasing, or selling the real estate, unless the primary business of the owner or lessor is providing real estate brokerage services; or
a person while acting in the capacity of:
a receiver;
a trustee;
a personal representative; or
a guardian.
